    possible between the xfs-log and xfs-cil workqueues. Consider the
    following codepath from xfs_log_worker():
    
    xfs_log_worker()
      xfs_log_force()
        _xfs_log_force()
          xlog_cil_force()
            xlog_cil_force_lsn()
              xlog_cil_push_now()
                flush_work()
    
